Cyber Claw:





A growl of Dinobot's tone of voice came from Cyber Claw. She didn't like him 
at all. All he was was a another Megatron, demanding her skills, telling her 
when to fight, when she had other things to do. So, he was saying fight or I 
tell you nothing. That slag!

"So, you take me for another one of your instruments?" meaning his troops. A 
barking laugh leapt from her mouth. "You're just another son of a 
maintanence bot like Megatron." She didn't know when to watch her mouth, 
that was the way she was sent on exile and hunted. "You seem to have more 
troops than you realize."
